Attendance data by school (SY 2009-2019)

attendance_msde_SY0919.Rd

Attendance data from the Maryland State Department of Education. Raw CSV data files with the full state enrollment data are available in the inst/extdata folder. Any percent variables with a value of 95 interpreted as equivalent at or above 95 value of 5 definitions are incomplete.

attendance_msde_SY0919

Format

A data frame with 3,197 rows and 15 variables:

school_year

School year or academic year, e.g. 2019 for 2019-2020 school year

school_number

School number (0 indicates all schools)

school_name

School name

grade_band

Grade band (school type)

attend_rate_pct

Attendance rate (percent)

days_attended_cnt

Count of days attended

days_member_cnt

double ... count

fewer_5_pct

double ... percent

fewer_5_cnt

double ... count

more_20_pct

double ... percent

more_20_cnt

double ... count

more_90_member_cnt

double ... count

chronic_absentee_cnt

Chronic absentee count

chronic_absentee_denom

Chronic absentee denominator

chronic_absentee_pct

Chronic absentee percent

Source

https://reportcard.msde.maryland.gov/Graphs/#/DataDownloads//3/17/6/99/XXXX/2019
